      "index": "a0",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 648239707,
      "version": 137,
      "versionNonce": 449086421,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1756826686742,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Stock trading platform like Zerodha\n\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Stock trading platform like Zerodha\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "mrnWRgE_PkH5quuQU9x2A",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 256.7999572753906,
      "y": 250.5,
      "width": 564.575439453125,
      "height": 380,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1370864405,
      "version": 684,
      "versionNonce": 217744379,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1756833645223,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional requirements\n\n- users should be able to place buy/sell orders for different instruments\n- support Limit and Market orders\n- users should be able to see the stock prices in real time\n    - optionally support historic rates and charts for instruments\n\n\n\nNon functional requirements\n\n- buy/sell should be highly consistent\n- instrument price and charts should be highly available\n- execution of orders should be fast/low-latency\n- scale to support 100M users\n\n\n\n ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional requirements\n\n- users should be able to place buy/sell orders for different instruments\n- support Limit and Market orders\n- users should be able to see the stock prices in real time\n    - optionally support historic rates and charts for instruments\n\n\n\nNon functional requirements\n\n- buy/sell should be highly consistent\n- instrument price and charts should be highly available\n- execution of orders should be fast/low-latency\n- scale to support 100M users\n\n\n\n ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "kaHV0OemO5fS-9-OfsCiB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 255.199951171875,
      "y": 586.1999816894531,
      "width": 361.11968994140625,
      "height": 540,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 962970741,
      "version": 575,
      "versionNonce": 1290311157,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1756833834293,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Back of the envelope estimations\n\n- 10% DAU = 10M users daily\nread heavy system\nper user keeps track of atleast 10 stocks,\nwatching 20 times per day\n= 10 ^ 7 x 10 x 20 =  2 B queries per day avg\n= 2 x 10^9 / 10^5 = 20,000 qps\n\npeak load = 200,000 qps\n\n\n\nCore entities\n- user\n- orders management service\n- pricing service\n- exchange gateway processor\n\n\n\nAPI\n- GET api/stockPrice -> time series data\n{\n    symbol = AAPL\n    timeframe = 5mins\n}",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Back of the envelope estimations\n\n- 10% DAU = 10M users daily\nread heavy system\nper user keeps track of atleast 10 stocks,\nwatching 20 times per day\n= 10 ^ 7 x 10 x 20 =  2 B queries per day avg\n= 2 x 10^9 / 10^5 = 20,000 qps\n\npeak load = 200,000 qps\n\n\n\nCore entities\n- user\n- orders management service\n- pricing service\n- exchange gateway processor\n\n\n\nAPI\n- GET api/stockPrice -> time series data\n{\n    symbol = AAPL\n    timeframe = 5mins\n}",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
